    <h3>Description of the to-do-list</h3>
    <p>Developed a to-do list application in Python leveraging its object-oriented programming capabilities. The application allows users to add tasks, mark them as complete, delete tasks, and display the list of pending and completed items. Implemented a user-friendly interface using Python's tkinter library for seamless interaction. Incorporated functionality to save tasks to a text file for persistence between sessions, ensuring that users can access their to-do list across multiple sessions."</p>
